msgstr ""

#. grow-green.flyer-section.description
#. +> trunk5
#: i18n/en.yaml:235
msgid "The \"Environmentally-Friendly Software?!\" leaflet provides an overview of the environmental harm driven by e-waste and hardware manufacturing – and how to combat it with Free & Open Source Software (FOSS). The leaflet is released under a Creative Commons licence, which means you can print and distribute it in your community now. Let your neighbors know why the most environmentally-friendly device is the one they already own!"
